title: Look At Starman Goooooo!
summary: I loved the original Kirby Air Ride and I absolutely enjoyed the Direct showing off the changes they made! The environment and Machines are so beautiful, that I just picked a random-ish spot in the Direct to redraw!

imgs.alt: Close of up a digital art piece, focusing on Starman from Kirby Air Riders, riding on a Wing Star, flying up into the sky towards the viewer. There is a dirt raceway track below them surrounded by grass and flowers. It's signed by "Gramophone Turtle".

Digital art piece of Starman from Kirby Air Riders, riding on a Wing Star, flying up into the sky towards the viewer. There is a dirt raceway track below them surrounded by grass and flowers, with trees and a blue sky in the distance. It's signed by "Gramophone Turtle".
